## Summary
This documentation explains how to build, analyze, and utilize predictions in Amplitude Activation to segment users based on their likelihood to perform future actions. It covers the prediction creation process, analyzing model performance through feature importance metrics, and creating predictive cohorts for targeting campaigns or further analysis.

